title: Looking for a support and jungle!
body:
Hey guys! 
A few friends and I are putting together a team to compete in tournies on the weekend. We vary in elo (Diamond mid, top plat and adc gold) but we want to learn and practice with each other. If anyone is interested in playing sup or jungle hmu! We would like to have people as soon as possible so we can practice (looking to play together 2ish times a week) And playing in tourny either every week or every other. 

For Support: We would like someone who plays varying champs. Some champs that sustain (IE type Nami) and some hard engage (IE Leona type). Looking for gold+
For jungle: Again someone who has varying champions. Some tanks and some carries. Pref plat+ 

Again let me know if you are interested! 
Thanks,
CP3 K9

replies.body: Im a solid jungle in mid gold, good winrate and great mechanics.
I'm a plat 4 jungle player that can play different styles of jungler I added you in game my ign is Blüsh
I am G3 Supp in solo and Plat 5 in flex. play many diff champs i.e thresh naut ali morgana brand sona etc.
